ENTRY            F1175   20260116   20260508   20260508       F108
SUBENT        F1175001   20260116   20260508   20260508       F108
BIB                  9         17
TITLE      Isobaric analogue states of 47Ca
AUTHOR     (C.Gaarde,K.Kemp,P.Wilhjelm)
INSTITUTE  (2DENNBI)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,102,1,1967)
           #doi:10.1016/0375-9474(67)90321-1
FACILITY   (VDG,2DENNBI) The 4 MeV Van de Graaff accelerator was
           used.
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Two silicon surface barrier detectors and
           a 2*256 pulse-height analyser were used.
SAMPLE     The 46Ca target with natural relative abundance of
           Ca - 0.0033% was used. The thickness in 46Ca was about
           15 ug/cm2. The isotopic purity was better than 99%.
           Inhomogeneities in the target thickness made it
           necessary to measure relative yields in two angles.
METHOD     (PHD)
HISTORY    (20121129C)
           (20260116A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              17
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           20
SUBENT        F1175002   20260116   20260508   20260508       F108
BIB                  4          7
REACTION   (20-CA-46(P,EL)20-CA-46,,DA,,RSD)
